Package: mojchart
Title: Colour palettes and formatting for ggplot2 charts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Graham",
           family = "Ison",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "graham.ison@justice.gov.uk")
Description: Provides functions for formatting charts in ggplot2.
    Colour palettes are based on MoJ corporate colours. All MoJ
    colours are also made available individually.
